title: Yvonne Strahovski
summary: Yvonne Jacqueline Strzechowski[1][2] (born 30 July 1982), known professionally as Yvonne Strahovski (/strəˈhɒvski/), is an Australian actress of television, film and theatre. Primarily noted for her roles in dramatic television, she has received numerous awards and nominations,[3] including two Primetime Emmy Award nominations and three Screen Actors Guild Award nominations.
